'''Hojiakbar Ulugʻbek oʻgʻli Alijonov''' (born 19 April 1997), known as ''Khojiakbar Alijonov'', is an Uzbek professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|right-back]] for [[Pakhtakor FC|Pakhtakor]] in the [[Uzbekistan Super League]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==Club career==
On 11 February 2026, [[Pakhtakor FC|Pakhtakor]] announced that they had extended their contract with Alijonov until the end of the 2027 season.<ref name="Khojiakbar Alijonov 2027">{{cite web |title=Ҳожиакбар Алижонов билан шартнома узайтирилди |url=https://t.me/Pakhtakor_FC/53494/ |website=telegram.me/s/Pakhtakor_FC |publisher=Pakhtakor FC Telegram |access-date=13 February 2026 |language=Uzbek |date=11 February 2026}}</ref>

==International career==
Alijonov made his debut for the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]] in a 4–0 friendly win over [[North Korea national football team|North Korea]] on 7 June 2019.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/23201/Uzbekistan_North_Korea.html|title=Uzbekistan vs. North Korea (4:0)|first=Benjamin|last=Strack-Zimmermann|website=www.national-football-teams.com}}</ref>

